->>> POPASL_EXCEPTIONS
@node POPASL_EXCEPTIONS "Exeptions"

   @{BG shine}Constructor@{BG back}

      "UTIL" will be raised if the utility.library v37+ can't be opened.
      "TYPE" will be raised if you pass a wrong value to PLA_PopAsl_Type.

   @{BG shine}message_action()@{BG back}

      "ASL"  will be raised if the asl.library v38+ can't be opened.
      "AREQ" will be raised if the plugin fails to allocate the asl
             request structure.

@endnode
